  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n1.  Redefine onboarding related qml objects creations and deletion and syncronize them correctly with the `startupModule` since now ui and backend are \"not syncronized\" so it is causing a crash when retranslating, since reevaluation of bindings are causing to  calling `startupModule` that is already null.\r\nAt least `OnboardingLayout.qml` should be destroyed after loggin as it is done with the `startupModule` instance.\r\n\r\n2. Revert https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/7822\r\n\r\nOnce it is done, ensure the app doesn't crash after changing language and it is dynamically updated on mac and windows.",
